column5: Thanks for the link Dan, i was just doing a little research myself from yesterdays experience's.
Your welcome..can't wait to try that rod ya sold me!
If ya look close, there are some great articles by a really handsome man on there
Well..don't keep us in suspenders?  Who..?? (Dan Reid wasn't on the list!)
Must have thrown you off with the handsome.. it's me.
Yessir Danbo I think there's a couple more. Before the criticism rolls in I wrote those articles when I was 17 so cut me some slack, lol
